Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Reality slips far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:44.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Fiction comes alive,we start to play it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hope is no more ,behind a closed door
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}As we drift away from where we were before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hope and hopelessness become one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's all meaningless ,we've already begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}yup, we are all one and the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:56.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Never opposites,we play the same game
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:58.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Walk the thin line between hope and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Running from the truth,but it's already here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Told so many lies, I dunno if they can find me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Only one life to live,so choose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Heads or tails,do you even know the side you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Doesn't really matter if it's on the same coin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:09.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If you wanna achieve you gotta believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's on right now, here's the door here's the key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:14.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2}The search is so very long, we let it fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:18.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}There's a ray of hope beyond despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:23.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Move on, look for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:25.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}In this world　　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:29.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Slip through the confusion, find a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Beat the twisted evil things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Just do it, go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:44.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Slip through the confusion, find a solution
